annotationA: Loquacious, isoform B; Loquacious (Loqs) is a double-stranded RNA binding protein with multiple splicing isoforms. Loqs-PB and Loqs-PA associate with Dcr-1 to facilitate processing of precursor miRNA into mature miRNA, whereas Loqs-PD interacts with Dcr-2 to enhance processing of dsRNA into siRNA
annotationB: Argonaute-1, isoform A; Argonaute-1 is an Argonaute/Piwi family protein, which interacts with microRNAs to form miRNA-induced silencing complexes (miRISCs). miRISCs are guided to target and repress mRNAs either by transcript destabilisation, translational inhibition, or both
